9, \"end\": 199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9986915619572839, \"rank\": 0.0012985284544691554, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"B-Girl Rachael 'Raygun' Gunn, 36, on Friday lost all three pool matches against the USA, France and Lithuania in the sport's opener at Paris' Place de la Concorde.\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 398, \"end\": 404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.433745178719196e-28, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}, {\"begin\": 406, \"end\": 410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.8402426580624789, \"rank\": 0.1854547187875912, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 466, \"end\": 469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9833906321843596, \"rank\": 0.015019504908479723, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 471, \"end\": 477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9990676617013049, \"rank\": 0.0009284637989297499, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 482, \"end\": 491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9998467246540854, \"rank\": 0.00015316567984473924, \"text\": \"Lithuania\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 517, \"end\": 522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.240820314716585e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 524, \"end\": 544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 8.163779171440817e-12, \"text\": \"Place de la Concorde\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans on social media slammed the Australian representative for her clumsy roll and wriggle on the floor resulting in the nation losing to Japan's gold medal B-Girl Ami.\", \"from\": 547, \"to\": 715, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 580, \"end\": 590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9986915619572839, \"rank\": 0.0012985284544691554, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 685, \"end\": 690, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9785510863424989, \"rank\": 0.019383041213960995, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Reminds me of when my dog has an ear infection and has to rub its head in the lawn,\\\" one person said on X of Raygun's performance.\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 827, \"end\": 833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.433745178719196e-28, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As an Australian, I 100% apologise for this embarrassment,\\\" said another.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 924, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 857, \"end\": 867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9986915619572839, \"rank\": 0.0012985284544691554, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have nothing funny to say about Rachael 'Raygun' Gunn.\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 983, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 961, \"end\": 968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.9999999998608473, \"rank\": 1.3847876275068243e-10, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her disgraceful performance has brought a great shame upon our nation,\\\" said another.\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1069, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A fourth person likened the athletes awkward act to \\\"6-year-olds after saying 'watch this'\\\".\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Enthusiasts also mocked Gunn's Australian Olympic tracksuit as her choice of uniform, a stark contrast to her competitor's hip streetwear styles.\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1189, \"end\": 1193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.8402426580624789, \"rank\": 0.1854547187875912, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1196, \"end\": 1206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9986915619572839, \"rank\": 0.0012985284544691554, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 36-year-old came head-to-head with the backlash on Saturday and took to Instagram stories with a fiery shot at her tormenters.\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1442, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1388, \"end\": 1397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1004876455887708e-35, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Looking forward to the same level of scrutiny on what the bboys wear tomorrow,\\\" she wrote over a yellow, green and blue gradient backdrop.\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Raygun earlier shared a post from the Australian breaking team in which she could be heard ranting about the importance of individuality.\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1623, \"end\": 1633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9986915619572839, \"rank\": 0.0012985284544691554, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Do not be afraid to be different,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1769, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Go out there and represent yourself, you never know where that's gonna take you.\\\"\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1853, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn glared down the camera and made a performative gesture with her hat before leaping out to eager crowds waiting for the Australian PHD candidate and university lecturer to make move in France's capital.\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 2061, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1855, \"end\": 1859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.8402426580624789, \"rank\": 0.1854547187875912, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1979, \"end\": 1989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9986915619572839, \"rank\": 0.0012985284544691554, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1990, \"end\": 1993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doctor_of_Philosophy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1014650761449166e-16, \"text\": \"PHD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doctor_of_Philosophy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doctor_of_Philosophy\"}, {\"begin\": 2044, \"end\": 2050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9990676617013049, \"rank\": 0.0009284637989297499, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The dancer is Australia's top-ranking breakdancer and a creative arts researcher specialising in the cultural politics of breakdancing at Sydney's Macquarie University.\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2231, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2077, \"end\": 2086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.6680540882085197, \"rank\": 0.3934049304581022, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2201, \"end\": 2207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.7842309205315738, \"rank\": 0.27513455789460883, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}, {\"begin\": 2210, \"end\": 2230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macquarie_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.92598113473628e-22, \"text\": \"Macquarie University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macquarie_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macquarie_University\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She secured her place in the Games as Australia's b-girl delegate after winning last year's Oceania Breaking Championships against a dancer named Molly.\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2271, \"end\": 2280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.6680540882085197, \"rank\": 0.3934049304581022, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2325, \"end\": 2332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceania\", \"score\": 0.9999941841884673, \"rank\": 3.33986980363794e-06, \"text\": \"Oceania\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceania\"}, {\"begin\": 2379, \"end\": 2384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Hayes\", \"score\": 0.9999999966375981, \"rank\": 3.207410395427757e-09, \"text\": \"Molly\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Hayes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Hayes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking to reporters after her Paris flop failed to maintain her status as a breaking great, Gunn admitted she was never going to win in 2024.\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2419, \"end\": 2424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.240820314716585e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2481, \"end\": 2485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.8402426580624789, \"rank\": 0.1854547187875912, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All my moves are original,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2570, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was never going to beat these girls on what they do best, the dynamic and the power moves, so I wanted to move differently, be artistic and creative because how many chances do you get in a lifetime to do that on an international stage?\", \"from\": 2572, \"to\": 2811, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was always the underdog and wanted to make my mark in a different way.\\\"\", \"from\": 2813, \"to\": 2887, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know how rare this opportunity is and I wanted to take the chance to wear the green and gold,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2889, \"to\": 2996, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not know why some of the other girls did not want to wear their kit.\", \"from\": 2998, \"to\": 3072, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a real moment of pride for me to wear the Australian uniform, I was particularly excited for this shirt to have the Indigenous print on the arms.\\\"\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3226, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3122, \"end\": 3132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9986915619572839, \"rank\": 0.0012985284544691554, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 3196, \"end\": 3206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indigenous_Australians\", \"score\": 0.9966600734836197, \"rank\": 0.0033505512990326014, \"text\": \"Indigenous\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indigenous_Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indigenous_Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After I have recovered, I will probably be writing about it.\\\"\", \"from\": 3228, \"to\": 3290, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sympathetic fans flooded social media with messages of support for the Australian.\", \"from\": 3292, \"to\": 3374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3363, \"end\": 3373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9986915619572839, \"rank\": 0.0012985284544691554, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Props to Raygun for having the guts to go out there,\\\" one person said.\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3386, \"end\": 3392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.433745178719196e-28, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Raygun from Australia is my Olympic hero actually,\\\" another added.\", \"from\": 3449, \"to\": 3516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3462, \"end\": 3471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.6680540882085197, \"rank\": 0.3934049304581022, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Breaking featured for the first time on the main Olympic stage and was welcomed with a booming introduction from US rapper Snoop Dogg.\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3652, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3631, \"end\": 3633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.958076311560773, \"rank\": 0.03846359787255943, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3641, \"end\": 3651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has faced much controversy and will not return for the 2028 Games in Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 3654, \"to\": 3738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3726, \"end\": 3737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.741407712674826e-16, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The sport will have one more moment in the spotlight on Sunday with Australia's 16-year-old B-boy Jeff (J Attack) Dunne set to front in the male competition at 12.17am.\", \"from\": 3740, \"to\": 3908, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3808, \"end\": 3817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.6680540882085197, \"rank\": 0.3934049304581022, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To join the conversation, pleaselog in.Do not have an account?Register  Join the conversation, you are commenting asLogout  Our Apps\", \"from\": 3910, \"to\": 4042, \"entities\": []}]}"